* snow Tech and Shadow Cat, getting no response from
the base, stepped out of the trees, hoping to get
someone's attention. Looking about, they spot Dark
Mouse frantically jumping up and down. snow Tech
looked at his sister,*

 " I hope that's not what WE have to do to get in."

 * Shadow Cat gave Snow Tech a dirty look and
replied,*

 " I don't think it's wise to attract attention to our
selves, there seems to be Predacons about, the mouse
registers as one and there are more approaching the
ship, i suggest we try again on the com-link."

 * Snow Tech Grumbles and pushes the com-link again,*

 " This is Snow Tech and Shadow Cat, we request
permission to enter, I repeat, we ask for permission
to enter, there are Predacons after us!"
